-- France's Schneider Looks for Australia Acquisitions, Financial Review Says
-- B y   J a c o b   G r e b e r
-- 2010-10-03T21:45:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-03/france-s-schneider-looks-for-australia-acquisitions-financial-review-says.html
France-based Schneider Electric SA is
searching Australia for acquisitions valued as much as 150
million euros, the Australian Financial Review said, citing an
interview with the company’s Asia-Pacific Managing director
Lionel Finidori.  Finidori said the company’s growth in Australia will be
between 7 percent and 8 percent this financial year, the
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jacob Greber in Sydney at 
